verbose_text: Compared with model group, the Bcl-2 protein expression level in 10 and 20 mg/kg TIIA groups and cleaved caspase-3 protein expression level in 5, 10 and 20 mg/kg TIIA groups were significantly increased, respectively (P < 0.05), and the Bax protein expression level in 5, 10 and 20 mg/kg TIIA groups was significantly decreased, respectively (P < 0.05) (XREF_FIG).
